<subSubSection box="[165,1370,963,996]" pageId="65" pageNumber="460" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="65.[165,1376,293,1467]" box="[165,1370,963,996]" pageId="65" pageNumber="460">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[165,401,963,996]" pageId="65" pageNumber="460">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Kelaart’s Long-clawed Shrew is semi-fossorial based on its long claws.
</paragraph>
